  <name>Create Icon Files</name>
  <summary>Automatically create the set of icon files for Linux, Windows, macOS, and Unix systems.</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Create Icon Files is a desktop application for quickly and accurately creating
      icon files from images. It provides a one-click workflow to generate all necessary icon files. 
      The application is designed for graphic designers, developers, and content creators who need to generate
      application icons in various sizes and formats.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Output icon files for Linux, Windows, macOS, and Unix systems</li>
      <li>icon.ico, icon.icns, icon.png, icon.svg, and the set of Linux icon files 16x16 to 512x512</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      The tool is optimized for accuracy and speed on modern desktops and can be used
      entirely offline once installed.
    </p>
  </description>

